import { getCurrentEvn } from "./common/utils/env"
import WebVolcengine from "./web" // web 端
import UniVolcengine from "./uni-app" // uni-app
import WxmpVolcengine from "./wxmp" // 微信小程序端
let analysisClass
const platform = getCurrentEvn()
switch (platform) {
  case "mp-weixin":
    analysisClass = WxmpVolcengine
    break
  case "web":
    analysisClass = WebVolcengine
    break
  default:
    analysisClass = UniVolcengine
}
export default analysisClass
